$ mathknow <dbl> NA, NA, NA, -0.11, -0.11, -0.11, -0.11, -0.11, -0.11, -0.11, …
$ housepov <dbl> 0.082, 0.082, 0.082, 0.082, 0.082, 0.082, 0.082, 0.082, 0.082…
